      <h1 class="display-5 mb-3">Social Security – Working Families Retirement Security and Solvency Bill (2027)</h1>
      <p class="lead mb-4">
        Secure Social Security for 75+ years without cutting benefits or raising the retirement age — funded by fair‑share contributions at the very top, protected by a lockbox, and strengthened with a seniors‑focused COLA and a minimum benefit floor.
      </p>
      <!-- Outcomes at a glance -->
      <div class="roi-wrap">
        <span class="roi-chip"><i class="fa-solid fa-piggy-bank"></i> 75+ Years Solvency</span>
