        <span class="roi-chip"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i> CPI‑E COLA</span>
        <span class="roi-chip"><i class="fa-solid fa-vault"></i> Trust‑Fund Lockbox</span>
        <span class="roi-chip"><i class="fa-solid fa-people-roof"></i> Minimum Benefit Floor</span>
